{"tid":1476720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黃台之瓜，何堪再摘」","createTime":"2019-08-16T02:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T02:04:12.000Z","uid":96540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5125e4d827f4d1d0cff8ea8e0ee56f2d52b8e7cf","tid":1476720,"uid":96540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:01:45.000Z","msg":"已退休的長和資深顧問李嘉誠，以「一個香港市民」身份在多份報章，分別刊登兩款全版廣告。其中一款廣告內容寫有「黃台之瓜，何堪再摘」，是出自武則天和唐高宗所生的第二個兒子李賢臨自殺前寫下的絕詩《黃台瓜辭》。<br />\n《黃台瓜辭》全詩為：「種瓜黃台下，瓜熟子離離。一摘使瓜好，再摘令瓜稀，三摘猶雲可，四摘抱蔓歸。」<br />\n當年在太子、李賢的兄長李弘死後，李賢一度被封為太子，其後武則天將李賢癈為庶人，李賢臨死前留下《黃台瓜辭》名詩，以黃台之瓜比喻唐代宗室，備受一次又一次的採摘，冀望勸告母親武則天，勿再對子女趕盡殺絕。惟李賢最後還是被武則天逼令自殺而終。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%8C%E9%BB%83%E5%8F%B0%E4%B9%8B%E7%93%9C%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%95%E5%A0%AA%E5%86%8D%E6%91%98%E3%80%8D%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E6%9D%8E%E8%B3%A2%E7%B5%95%E8%A9%A9%E3%80%8A%E9%BB%83%E5%8F%B0%E7%93%9C%E8%BE%AD%E3%80%8B-185055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%258F%25B0%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%2593%259C%25EF%25BC%258C%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25A0%25AA%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2591%2598%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%259D%258E%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E7%25B5%2595%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E3%2580%258A%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2593%259C%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E3%2580%258B-185055&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=10a5419c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%8C%E9%BB%83%E5%8F%B0%E4%B9%8B%E7%93%9C%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%95%E5%A0%AA%E5%86%8D%E6%91%98%E3%80%8D%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E6%9D%8E%E8%B3%A2%E7%B5%95%E8%A9%A9%E3%80%8A%E9%BB%83%E5%8F%B0%E7%93%9C%E8%BE%AD%E3%80%8B-185055</a>"},{"pid":"23a2bf056e5586307f4c175ac23ca514ed4d6a64","tid":1476720,"uid":96540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:03:52.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc423c5aa67c203e9326e1bae24d4eb0904cfac2","tid":1476720,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"黃台仰"}]}